### Podocytes
- Scanning electron microscopy image of a portion of the glomerulus.
- Glomerulus: filtering unit of the kidney.
  - Composed of a network of capilaries.
  - Filtrates pass through the pores in the capillaries, basin material, and reach the podocytes.
- Each of the bumps is a cell body.








